            "text": "<h6><strong>\"I love these sneakers.</strong><br/>I love these sneakers. I have bought three of the same sneakers, but in different colors. What a difference they have made on my feet. I like to take my dog for walks. I had to stop. My feet were in such pain. With these sneakers my feet are fine now. Thank you Aetrex.</h6>",
